snippet.title: Contra: the War of the Worlds / 魂斗罗 星际战争 (Mobile, j2me) Longplay
snippet.description:
Contra: the War of the Worlds (魂斗罗 星际战争) was released by Konami Shanghai in 2009 exclusively in China. It is official Contra game for j2me celphones and it's only game for this platform which is not port or remake of different game. It's very neat game with gameplay features from Contra III: the Alien Wars and its own gimmics, such as healthbar, low gravity zone, autoscrolling level and completely new plot and settings. Finally, we fights aliens on Moon!
This game is also known as Contra: Planet Force, Contra: Interstellar Battle and Contra: Star Wars.
